{"tid":2221611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［陳生要機票嗎］香港航空： 為方便有需要去台灣既旅客 10月15起會恢復飛台航班","createTime":"2020-09-28T13:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T13:47:18.000Z","uid":22556,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bbd76041fd5e3e373ac263bbac2ca47f3aa6af06","tid":2221611,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T13:22:02.000Z","msg":"【恢復航班 - #台北航線】<br />\nService resumes to #Taipei<br />\n<br />\n為方便赴台學生及有需要往返港台嘅旅客，我哋將會由2020年10月15日起，恢復香港往來台北嘅航班，並逢每週四出發*！而上海浦東、北京及馬尼拉航線，亦已重新投入服務，以方便不同旅客計劃行程。<br />\n了解更多：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/HKA_TPE_Flights_TC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKA_TPE_Flights_TC&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=25d323e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HKA_TPE_Flights_TC</a> <br />\n<br />\n* 以上航班計劃可能有所變化，請以香港航空官網最新航班動態為準。<br />\n<br />\nIn response to travel demands, service between Hong Kong and Taipei will resume every Thursday from 15 October 2020. Flights between Shanghai Pudong, Beijing, and Manila are also available now.<br />\nLearn more at <a href=\"http://bit.ly/HKA_TPE_Flights_EN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKA_TPE_Flights_EN&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=f1827cca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/HKA_TPE_Flights_EN</a> <br />\n<br />\n* Flight schedules may subject to change, please refer to the latest flight status on Hong Kong Airlines official website.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/124470254262656/posts/3414477498595232/?extid=2yKC0oWbQPksgHbB&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F124470254262656%2Fposts%2F3414477498595232%2F%3Fextid%3D2yKC0oWbQPksgHbB%26d%3Dn&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=be511fc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/124470254262656/posts/3414477498595232/?extid=2yKC0oWbQPksgHbB&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"2949132802791